{"tid":1150684,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"棕熊疑似拿骨頭賄賂家犬 好讓自己安心翻垃圾","createTime":"2019-05-12T04:55:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-12T07:46:09.000Z","uid":22675,"like":30,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"5381949e1fed192dfc2c19c026611dd045895a35","tid":1150684,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T04:55:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/05/12/g3VJDA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F05%2F12%2Fg3VJDA.jpg&h=cbb85fb7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n熊仔好聰明！加拿大男子喬丹（Jesse Jordan）養了一隻大型犬布里克伯里（Brickleberry），牠被訓練成晚上對闖進院子裡的入侵者吠叫，但某天喬丹突然發現愛犬在啃憑空跑出來的骨頭，原本裝好的垃圾更是撒了一地，因此懷疑可能是熊仔拿鹿骨賄賂狗仔，這樣才可以安靜地翻垃圾找殘餘食物。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n據《福斯新聞》報導，喬丹表示，從那天發生這起奇怪的事件之後，到現在已經有3次類似情況出現了，所以他認為熊仔已經學會拿骨頭讓汪星人不要汪汪叫。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n喬丹將此事分享到推特後，有網友開始擔心拴在外面的狗仔是否安全，喬丹則拍胸脯保證，在安大略省北方的棕熊通常不會是威脅，只是一種很麻煩的動物。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n一名網友則打趣地說，從這些事情看起來，顯然喬丹平常沒有讓布里克伯里好好享受過，所以熊熊一旦提供更好的交易（骨頭），那麼狗仔就會欣然接受，這就是資本主義的力量。"},{"pid":"067cbc2ec96c3fa9c5888f17ceb49feb8d6917ce","tid":1150684,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T04:56:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2787597\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2787597&d=0a%2BBnfQRLGMOm4peNIjNW6Zg5fsFimH5gYFReGFrXmU%3D&h=fd603545\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2787597&h=90bcd9a1\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2787597</a>"},{"pid":"cb3cdb91144537d504a4fa8d0e381f2cdc862125","tid":1150684,"uid":28765,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T04:56:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://m1080.com/upimg/zyzp1/72214.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm1080.com%2Fupimg%2Fzyzp1%2F72214.jpg&h=8194c0a1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e6e5efddfbfb30c6290be40a6aa5dc368e1107f